"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-imane-khelif-anja-stridsman-boxing-paris-b2594064.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  In 2019, Anja Stridsman was a decision winner against Khelif, who boxes for Olympic gold on Friday  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Anja Stridsman, a former opponent ofImane Khelif, has called criticism of the Olympic boxer \\\"ignorant and stupid\\\".\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has been at the centre of a gender rowatParis 2024, having reached the welterweight gold-medal match, a year afterallegedly failing a gender eligibility test.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif, 25, was disqualified from the 2023 World Championships due to the presence of certain chromosomes, the InternationalBoxingAssociation (IBA) said on Monday (5 August).\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9992842956195301, \"rank\": 0.0007159527765824285, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However,despite many baseless claims online, the Algerian has never identified as transgender or intersex.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.8602083370527963, \"rank\": 0.16131615759113388, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In any case, Khelif's victories in Paris -including her 46-second win over Italy Carini, who withdrew from their fight and broke down in tears - have proven controversial.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999530546131, \"rank\": 4.694540981806406e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.956549702449015, \"rank\": 0.041363967843802425, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999226196541281, \"rank\": 7.738633396926492e-05, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday night (9 August),Khelif boxes for gold against China's Liu Yang, and before that fight, Stridsman spoke to theAustralian Broadcasting Corporationabout her own experience in the ring with Khelif.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8949630495168832, \"rank\": 0.09537648924004269, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4189976457323682e-15, \"text\": \"Liu Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Stridsman, a 2018 Commonwealth Champion who beat Khelif on points in 2019, said: \\\"I do remember people saying to me: 'Oh, she looks like a bloke,' you know?\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8166807596141922, \"rank\": 0.18450963470653417, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"score\": 0.9999989851847351, \"rank\": 1.000507273704707e-06, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are fighting a bloke,' which I think is quite ignorant and stupid.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember not being very impressed with her, thinking that she wasn't using her reach, you know?\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not have a good jab,\\\" Stridsman said, before adding that Khelif has improved since they fought.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Per the Daily Mail, reporting from Australia, Stridsman also said: \\\"She wasn't particularly strong.\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\", \"score\": 0.9999596708436632, \"rank\": 4.0330782767712704e-05, \"text\": \"Daily Mail\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Mail\"}, {\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8166807596141922, \"rank\": 0.18450963470653417, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps a bit angry, but people get into this sport for different reasons.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember people commenting to me, 'Surely she's a man,' and, 'Good on you for beating a man,' and it angered me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stridsman is not the only former opponent of Khelif to address the Algerian's place in the sport.\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.8602083370527963, \"rank\": 0.16131615759113388, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amy Broadhurst,who beat Khelif at the 2022 World Championships, said: \\\"Personally I do not think she has done anything to 'cheat'.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2229, \"end\": 2243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"score\": 0.9999949375263346, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amy Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's the way she was born and that's out of her control.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that she has been [beaten] by nine females before says it all.\\\"\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA, which disqualified Khelif at the 2023 World Championships, no longer oversees boxing at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2503, \"end\": 2506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9992842956195301, \"rank\": 0.0007159527765824285, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisation was dropped by the International Olympic Committee before Tokyo 2021,due to fears of corruption and concerns over the body's finances and links to Russia.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2686, \"end\": 2691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8038067685900815, \"rank\": 0.244079872452397, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2775, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.7003221858048116, \"rank\": 0.31022855281613076, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wiki